profile:
Since 1992, Trico Homes has built new single and multi-family homes, offering a diverse selection of starter, move-up and semi-estate homes in Calgary, Airdrie, Chestermere, Cochrane, DeWinton and Okotoks. Whether you're looking for a quick possession or something more personalized, Trico’s team of dedicated staff will ensure you’ll find the perfect house to call home.

At Trico, we start every single day with one goal in mind; to deliver incredible life-changing moments. We know Calgarians have choices when buying a home. That’s why we’ve built a company that builds so much more than quality houses.

In the many years since Trico built our first home, our city has grown and so has our love for it. Along the way, we’ve become one of Calgary’s top builders - building over 11,500 single and multi-family homes and earning a reputation for our design, craftsmanship and customer care. Trico has received numerous accolades, including a Platinum member status as one of Canada’s 50 Best Managed Companies, Canada’s Best Workplaces, Canada's Top Small & Medium Employers, and a CHBA Excellence in Housing award. We are also proud to be Western Canada’s first and only homebuilder to become a certified B Corporation.

We’re committed to our industry and our city. We want to make our mark. To become a legacy company. We do more than develop quality homes. We help develop the place we call home.

Trico Homes. The Heart of Homebuilding.®
